  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can change your appearance at will, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.oj36nfak6jc2s5ky]{Disguise Self} with a caster level equal to your oracle level.</p>\n<p>At 7th level, you can choose to actually transform, which works the same way but counts as a polymorph effect instead of an illusion and doesnâ€™t allow a Will save to disbelieve.</p>\n<p>At 11th level, the ability lasts until you dismiss it or use it again, allowing you to even keep it active while you sleep.</p>\n<p>At 15th level, when you use this ability as a polymorph effect, you can gain the size bonus to your ability scores and additional racial abilities as if using @Compendium[pf1.spells.kouqz0pm1xl8xilm]{Alter Self}.</p>",
